  "_meta": {
    "description": "Per-port operational baselines for the multimodal logistics engine.",
    "source_notes": [
      "Numbers are steady-state medians derived from UNCTAD Review of Maritime Transport,",
      "IHS Markit/Journal of Commerce port congestion trackers, and public port authority",
      "annual reports (2023-2024). Where a UN/LOCODE is not listed the engine falls back to",
      "the default tier baseline shown below.",
      "Admin can override any of these via PUT /api/logistics/port_ops."
    ],
